OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784146709
OL,3,CSpain beat World Cup favourites France
OL,4,Cto secure place in final
OL,6,FSpain have beaten France, the
OL,7,Ftournament favourites, to reach their
OL,8,Ffirst World Cup final in 16 years.
OL,10,FIt was a decisive win by Spain with a
OL,11,Ffinal score of 2-0 thanks to goals
OL,12,Ffrom Mikel Oyarzabal and Pedro Porro.
OL,14,FOyarzabal's 22nd-minute penalty ` his
OL,15,Ffifth goal of the tournament ` coupled
OL,16,Fwith Tottenham full-back Porro's
OL,17,Fsecond-half finish secured a win for
OL,18,Fthe European champions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
