PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784146709
OL,3,CSpain beat World Cup favourites France
OL,4,Cto secure place in final
OL,6,FSpain will go on to play Argentina or
OL,7,FEngland in the World Cup final on
OL,8,FSunday, having come a long way since
OL,9,Ftheir nil-nil draw with Cape Verde in
OL,10,Ftheir first game of the tournament.
OL,12,FIt will be the second time Spain have
OL,13,Fmade it to the World Cup final, having
OL,14,Fwon the tournament in 2010 by beating
OL,15,Fthe Netherlands 1-0.
OL,17,FSpain had already beaten France in the
OL,18,F2024 European Championship semi-finals
OL,19,Fand again in Nations League play last
OL,20,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/3
