OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784146709
OL,3,CSpain beat World Cup favourites France
OL,4,Cto secure place in final
OL,6,FThe match was French manager Didier
OL,7,FDeschamps' last game after 14 years at
OL,8,Fthe helm - he is one of just three men
OL,9,Fto ever win the World Cup as both a
OL,10,Fplayer (1998) and a manager (2018).
